<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h3 id="head-d76f5294638a1d5c8a8f79dc4904894706df2a36">You know you've been playing too much ToME when</h3>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 You're on your way home from work and the traffic backs up on the freeway AFTER you get on the offramp so it doesn't slow you down and then the traffic light is green at the bottom of the offramp and your first thought is ...The RNG is being too nice to me, I wonder how I'm going to have to pay for this later? 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You forget that in The Lord of the Rings, Sauron didn't have the One Ring. (This really happened to me once -- <a href="./NeilStevens">NeilStevens</a>) 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 There are insects in your room bothering you, and you start thinking "Well, I can't do much bare-handed damage, but if I only had a crossbow around, you little bugs would be sorry!" (happened to <a href="./DanielJoo">DanielJoo</a>, when he was trying to study in the middle of the night since he has spent the day playing Tome) 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 When you dream about being in your house, the walls are #'s and the door is a 8 -- <a href="./SoulWynd">SoulWynd</a> 2004-07-11 05:45:45 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You think you *can* hold 25 elephants in your backpack on your way home. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You think you *should* 25 elephants in your backpack on your way home, being a possessor and summoner and all that. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You forget to feed your pets. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You forget to sleep. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You forget to eat or breathe, knowing you have enough healing magic to get you going for a week or so anyhow. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You put slime all over you and try to order it around. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You hunt rabbit for weeks and are unhappy when each rabbit has only 4 feet instead of the usual 6, only one being lucky. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 Your wife is part of the daily ultimate winner wife support group! 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 Your wife is part of the lost soul wife support group, and wished she'd be part of the ultimate winner wife support group; those husbands are at least happy! 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You discarded the engagement ring after reading the initials, claiming it's useless. Your wife is suddenly *ANGRY*! 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You wear "pink rabbit slippers of great luck" but feel misunderstood for it. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You are followed by some pets you intend to use as food. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You expect your cat to become more powerful after he catches a few mice. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You hand your wife a ring of confusion resistance (she said she was confused about you) 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 Roaches have taken over your apartment because you're just about to farm them for XP. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 When you see pharmaceutical commercials, you expect those pills to bring instant cures. And you say: side effects? What side effects?? 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You refer to certain politicians as "Morgoth", "fumblefingers", "Groo", or "Simon the weak agent of the black market". 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You haven't removed your clothes in weeks, ever! 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You start to believe in reincarnation - you've been so many people already... 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You heat ustensils so that they don't feel deathly cold! 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You go on rampages and steal at the store whenever it's open; not thinking of police arrests or anything. 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You start to want contact with the black market, and expect it to be always safe!!! 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You have excellent excuses for not cleaning the defenseless mold off your shower enclosure. -- <a href="./MayLith">MayLith</a> 2004-07-15 17:50:49 
</p>
</li>
    <li class="gap">
<p>
 You're still reading this. Yow! 
</p>
</li>
</ul>

